  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to test a brief education program for oncology nurses, to
      enhance their skills for managing psychosocial stressors associated with providing direct
      patient care. The investigators will explore efficacy of the intervention for reducing
      psychological stress and medical errors.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
